window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the seventh book of the Boy, Bye series titled the “G’ Spot, from ANS-Top-Shelf Bookz continue with the urban drama and fresh, hot passion flowing from the streets of Philly-town to the glam and glitter of LA. and New York with the unstoppable fresh face of the 187-Fresh Girl’s Lesa-Lesa, the Puerto Rican Flame. She is on fire like a supernova! </p> <p>She is just coming off her land, marking Latin tour-breaking records. She’s fresh, she’s hot, she’s young and muy bonito! Her debut album entitled Lesa G. the Puerto Rican Flame! And her multi-talented dance skills place her on a whole other level! She’s talk on the entertainment lips and airwave. Lesa-Lesa was already a hot young Puerto Rican woman who had many people, mostly guys calling her name twice. The tension is building, the drama is raising scams, and Jealousy, seduction, and cons are being plotted out! The feeling of Philly is about to change because it is about to get a whole lot chillier in Philly</p>"; 
